block content
  body(style="background-image: url(images/box.gif); background-repeat:no-repeat; background-size:1650px 1520px")
    #banner.page-header
      .row
        .col-lg-50
          h1
            | HELLO CINEPHILES ! WELCOME TO FRIENDS & FLIX....
            small Â Gathering all cinephile in platform...
      
        p.lead
          | Looking for wifi and a seat? Loc8r helps you find places to work when out and about. Perhaps with coffee, cake or a pint? Let Loc8r help you find the place you're looking for.
    #about.page-section
      .row
        .col-lg-12
          h2 Meet the Team
          p Friends & Flix is a platform created by passionate cinephiles who want to share their love for movies with other like-minded people. We believe that watching movies is more than just entertainment, it's a way of connecting, learning, and exploring new perspectives. That's why we created Friends & Flix, a place where you can find and join movie clubs, chat with other movie lovers, and discover new films to watch.
        .col-lg-6.col-md-6.col-sm-12
          .card.team-card
            img.card-img-top(src="images/founder.jpg", alt="Founder")
            .card-body(style="background-color:	 #476b6b ; color: white;")
              h3.card-title John Doe
              h4.card-subtitle Founder and CEO
              p.card-text John is the visionary behind Friends & Flix. He has been a movie buff since he was a kid, and he always dreamed of creating a community where people can share their passion for cinema. He is responsible for the overall direction and strategy of the platform, as well as leading the development team.
            .card-footer.social-icons
              a(href="#") <i class="fa fa-facebook"></i>
              a(href="#") <i class="fa fa-twitter"></i>
              a(href="#") <i class="fa fa-linkedin"></i>
        .col-lg-6.col-md-6.col-sm-12
          .card.team-card
            img.card-img-top(src="images/cofounder.jpg", alt="Co-founder")
            .card-body(style="background-color: black; color: white;")
              h3.card-title Jane Doe
              h4.card-subtitle Co-founder and CMO
              p.card-text Jane is the co-founder and chief marketing officer of Friends & Flix. She is an avid movie fan who loves to explore different genres and cultures through films. She is in charge of the marketing and branding of the platform, as well as managing the content and community team.
